replyContent: We only get a location that is accurate to around 50 meters from the phone, as it does location detection via cell tower or wifi detection to save battery.  There are often cases where you may be at a strip mall where there are multiple stores nearby and we simply can't get it right 100% of the time.  We do try to make it easy to change in the app.
